  17 Dec 2012; Hans de Graaff <graaff@gentoo.org> -rest-client-1.6.7.ebuild:
  Cleanup.

  15 Sep 2012; Hans de Graaff <graaff@gentoo.org> -rest-client-1.5.1.ebuild,
  -rest-client-1.6.1.ebuild, -rest-client-1.6.3.ebuild:
  Cleanup.

  14 Aug 2012; Diego E. Pettenò <flameeyes@gentoo.org> metadata.xml:
  Update metadata.xml so that it's the same as most other packages.

  13 Aug 2012; Diego E. Pettenò <flameeyes@gentoo.org>
  rest-client-1.6.7-r1.ebuild:
  Disable the automagic use of ruby-debug and mandatory use of rspec 1.x, then
  use the rspec recipe for tests. This allows dropping the jeweler dependency
  during tests at least.

